WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.933 --> 00:00:04.966
Your Majesty, Empress Dowager, urgent news.

2
00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:07.666
Bring up the previous evidence.

3
00:00:12.933 --> 00:00:15.200
Greetings to His Majesty and the Empress Dowager.

4
00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:18.600
We are unsure of the reason for your visit, Your Majesty and Empress Dowager.

5
00:00:18.700 --> 00:00:21.500
Repeat what you just said.

6
00:00:21.966 --> 00:00:23.866
I want to accuse Consort Rong.

7
00:00:24.133 --> 00:00:25.266
Of treason.

8
00:00:25.666 --> 00:00:27.566
Consort Rong has long been betrothed.

9
00:00:27.566 --> 00:00:29.300
She has long lost her chastity.

10
00:00:29.333 --> 00:00:32.166
I have never made a betrothal agreement.

11
00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:33.600
Stop your excuses.

12
00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:35.300
My mother heard from my grandmother

13
00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:36.500
That Consort Rong was engaged to

14
00:00:36.533 --> 00:00:40.400
Minister Shen Wu of the Ministry of Justice.

15
00:00:40.400 --> 00:00:41.400
It can't be false.

16
00:00:41.900 --> 00:00:43.066
Long Fei,

17
00:00:43.933 --> 00:00:44.733
Is this true?

18
00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:46.500
Reply to the Emperor.

19
00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:47.633
This subject has never been betrothed.

20
00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:49.833
When I was 13, my father asked me

21
00:00:50.166 --> 00:00:52.333
If I had a suitor.

22
00:00:52.333 --> 00:00:55.266
I said no.

23
00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:56.466
Not long after,

24
00:00:56.466 --> 00:00:57.500
My father passed away.

25
00:00:57.566 --> 00:00:59.000
Impossible.

26
00:00:59.000 --> 00:00:59.866
You and Shen Wu have been childhood sweethearts.

27
00:01:00.866 --> 00:01:02.700
And you both were raised by your grandfather.

28
00:01:02.700 --> 00:01:04.366
I suspect

29
00:01:04.366 --> 00:01:05.500
That you two

30
00:01:05.666 --> 00:01:06.533
Have already been involved privately.

31
00:01:06.533 --> 00:01:09.066
You’re being ridiculous.

32
00:01:09.066 --> 00:01:09.866
You can spread rumors,

33
00:01:10.966 --> 00:01:11.733
But I dare not slander my grandfather.

34
00:01:11.733 --> 00:01:13.900
If you keep this up,

35
00:01:13.900 --> 00:01:15.266
I’ll kill you.

36
00:01:18.466 --> 00:01:19.633
Please, Your Majesty, see clearly.

37
00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:21.666
My father was upright and honorable.

38
00:01:21.866 --> 00:01:24.300
If he had betrothed me to Shen Wu,

39
00:01:24.300 --> 00:01:26.166
It would be laughed at by the world.

40
00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:27.733
The Shen family would not come looking.

41
00:01:27.733 --> 00:01:30.566
That’s because you have already entered the palace.

42
00:01:30.566 --> 00:01:33.200
The Shen family doesn’t dare approach you.

43
00:01:40.766 --> 00:01:42.366
Your Majesty, Shen Wu.

44
00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:44.600
I ask you, do you have any betrothal agreement with Consort Rong?
